Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.35,0:00:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管回忆溢满心头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.60,0:00:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓在干掉的泪痕中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.01,0:01:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.22,0:01:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会以迎接朋友的方式\N温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我考上的是三流私立大学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.88,0:01:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我总算成为大学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着应该是过着\N快乐的大学生活,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字是这么拼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要闹了!\N明天我有模拟考!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,五代,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你,回去念补习班吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#06 春天的冲击!响子的秘密!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为你在打瞌睡\N没想到突然站起来大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天有模拟考!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经是大学生了\N居然还在作重考生时代的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你的重考生生活\N真的很悲惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你醒着吗?五代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,就算是春天\N也不能老是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近每晚都睡不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会睡不着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,都是管理员不让我睡好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五…五代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐,难道你跟那个美女管理员…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是每天晚上?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶不了你!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别傻了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到现在连管理员的手\N都还没牵过耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么说是她不让你睡好的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她每晚都出现在我的梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦得正好的时候就醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就半睡半醒的\N蒙蒙眬胧到天亮睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真凄惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至…至少想牵牵她的手!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我已经上了大学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天到了,樱花也绽放了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有季节改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的完全没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你回来得真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,因为下午停课
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出来散步吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,因为惣一郎缺乏运动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有这么幽静的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才都没有人经过耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:05:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,不可以!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以乱吃那个!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,你要去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得我好像被她拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,你也真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,这么说来就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等你耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员室的电话从刚才响个不停\N会不会是什么重要的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤太郎\N惣一郎拜托你照顾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟管理员在一起啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经是大学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么时候你才会记住啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你一点都没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟管理员出去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题问得非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去了哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在一条幽静无人的小路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溜狗散步对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它还有什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是我看错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看错什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前些时候我还以为\N管理员对你有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果考完试之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她根本对你不理不睬嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,这对母子真叫人讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没错\N我就知道是你打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个星期天吗?\N好,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么等你来罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有改变的只有你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之濑太太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话啊,电话\N有什么重要的事,不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老公…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的,下星期天\N一刻馆的房东听说要来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?房东?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不知道会不会稍微乖一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,我跟你说\N事情不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下星期天房东听说要来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几年没来的房东特地跑来耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说房东要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔你个头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东到底要来做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房租我都有按时缴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能只是随便来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:12:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此\N我们告诉五代一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样\N你觉得如何?五代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有听到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干嘛聚集到我的房间来?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道房东来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是来赶走恶房客的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是要调涨房租\N没有必要特地跑来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是这栋公寓太破旧了\N想改建成新大楼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个星期天…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题的星期天到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一成不变的春天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了一件\N宛如被芥末呛到的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是签房租契约时的那个老头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是房东
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少对我来说是个震撼事件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么?太没礼貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…爸爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你是房东的女儿啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉其中有阴谋…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是来\N暗中调查恶房客的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会搬出这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里有鬼的人\N才会说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临,伯父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那位重考生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父,我已经是大学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又叫他伯父了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子在干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,不要站在这里说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就进去休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁子也进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用,我在这里等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥陪你玩吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁子,不要麻烦人家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦\N听大人讲话也蛮无聊的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,不好意思\N麻烦你陪她一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那么我们上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍马屁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么伯父嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天真的到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来气色不错,我放心多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在这里可以转换心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是,因为这里怪人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,一定是这个缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,坐垫给你,还有可乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢,大哥哥你好好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代我向楼下的爸爸问好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是他的孙女喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爷爷腰不好,所以要我陪他来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说,你是管理员的侄女吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害,猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今年几岁了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这么年轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看起来有那么成熟吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你感觉蛮成熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,管理员她几岁呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子婶婶?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪到腰了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气变暖和了所以我就很放心\N好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你出门会不会太勉强了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,你想去见惣一郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁子,爸爸的腰又痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?\N都已经来到这里了说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们不介意的话\N让我陪你们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶好耶,跟我们一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打扰你们全家团聚\N那我就不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想麻烦一个外人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外人?太见外了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我叫您一声爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你跟他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你别乱说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉,难得的星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婶婶,他好像对我有意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他对我好温柔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是当真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你再怎么亲切\N我也不会把孙女嫁给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你出了社会\N再来我家正式拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是来扫墓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水这样够吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁子,过去好好祭拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你也去上个香好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是\N毕竟这也是一种缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问,这是哪位?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,我的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我儿子惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得对响子来说真的很残忍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫁过来还不到半年的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才半年的时间\N惣一郎就过世了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.97,0:21:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的到这里就可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的,上坡之后还要回转\N很麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你的帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.01,0:21:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.18,0:21:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.32,0:22:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人如果还活着\N或许会渐渐发现很多缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是,死去的人是天下无敌的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且,只在一起生活半年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:22:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们之间的回忆在她内心\N逐渐扩大成为她的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.34,0:22:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.61,0:23:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,千万不能逃避现实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.75,0:23:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的惣一郎已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会变成一个好男人\N保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.86,0:23:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.56,0:23:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要好好地往前看,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着前方向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.53,0:23:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地看着前方…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,走路要看着前方才行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫的名字叫惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.33,0:23:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.80,0:23:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他永远活在我的心里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:24:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回\N‘五代烦恼不已!响子喜欢的人’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎\N和你一起度过的快乐时光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.85,0:24:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.00,0:24:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何你能如此若无其事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.31,0:24:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光只是眨个眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.31,0:24:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能让我悸动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.45,0:24:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我身陷险境
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.59,0:24:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经可以相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.20,0:25:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏时机还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.61,0:25:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快要忍受不了\N快要变成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.12,0:25:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是痛苦的折磨

